Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.02,0:24:30.99,TitleEP,en,0,0,225,,Kaboom!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.02,0:24:30.99,TitleEP,en,0,0,85,,Karakuri Stronghold
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.02,0:24:30.99,NoteOnAnime,en,0,60,30,,{\an3\fs32}Look forwards for it!